# Shift Planning Domain Rules

## Overview

NesPrep is a shift planning system for Israeli businesses. It handles Hebrew text, Israeli work week (Sunday-Saturday), and specific shift patterns.

---

## Hebrew Day Names

```python
HEBREW_DAYS = ["ראשון", "שני", "שלישי", "רביעי", "חמישי", "שישי", "שבת"]

# Short forms commonly used
# א = ראשון (Sunday)
# ב = שני (Monday)
# ג = שלישי (Tuesday)
# ד = רביעי (Wednesday)
# ה = חמישי (Thursday)
# ו = שישי (Friday)
```

